<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .container {
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #007BFF;
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }

    .thank-you {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #4CAF50;
    }

    .info {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
  <h1>Thanks for your purchase!</h1>
  
  <p class="thank-you">Hi <%= @order.name %>,</p>
  
  <p>We are getting your order ready to be shipped. Once shipped, our system will send you an email with the UPS tracker, and your order will be delivered within 3 weeks from the order date. You can find your attachment below:</p>
  <div class="info">
  <a class="btn" href="<%= @pdf_url %>">Save As PDF</a>
</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
